  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nRight now when serving ReqResp block methods we read from DB, deserialize from bytes to struct and then re-serialize to send over the wire.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nWe could just serve the bytes stream directly from db, prevent any serdes and require no memory.",
